## Model

Delegate to subagents when the task allows, specifying model in the Agent tool:

- Explore (model="haiku"): find files, understand code, read without editing
- Plan: design before implementing on complex tasks
- general-purpose (model="sonnet"): scoped implementation, 2-3 files

**Dedicated agents** (`.claude/agents/`):

- `doc-updater` (sonnet, green): verify and update docs pre-commit
- `git-ops` (haiku, yellow): get git status/diff/log — read-only
- `migration-checker` (haiku, orange): validate SQL conventions pre-commit
[UI_REVIEWER_AGENT]

